### Enhancements

* Depend on standalone conda-index instead of bundled indexing code. (#4690)

### Bug fixes

* <news item>

### Deprecations

* `conda-build index --file` is no longer supported.
* `conda-build index --hotfix-source-repo` is removed.
* Prefer `python -m conda_index`, instead of `conda-build index` or `conda
  index`, to use faster indexing code.

